Package projects.spatial.knnutils

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PriorityQueue<T>
    PriorityQueue is an interface specification for Priority Queues.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BoundedPriorityQueue<T>
    BoundedPriorityQueue is a priority queue whose number of elements is bounded.
    BoundedPriorityQueueTests
    A testing framework for BoundedPriorityQueues.
    KNNComparator<T extends KDPoint>
    KNNComparator is a Serializable Comparator used for sorting KDPoints based on the KDPoint.distance(KDPoint, KDPoint) to an anchor KDPoint.
    NNData<T>
    NNData is a simple "struct-like" class that stores intermediate results of nearest neighbor queries.
    PriorityQueueNode<T>
    A PriorityQueueNode is a Comparable type which is used to wrap around the (data, priority) pairs in a PriorityQueue.
